CHANGES IN VERSION 1.1.4
-----------------------
* bowtie2 version updated to 2.4.4
* Able to build large bowtie indexes (.bt21)
* Able to align against large bowtie indexes (.bt2l)
* Able to create bam alignment files
* Use the bowtie2 and bowtie2-build wrapper scripts rather than the binaries directly

CHANGES IN VERSION 1.0.0
-----------------------
INITIAL RELEASE
* bowtie2 version 2.3.2
* AdapterRemoval version 2.2.1a 
